quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  33,69,"You who believe, do not be like those who abused Moses. cleared him of what they said. He became outstanding with God"
  33,70,"who believe, heed God and speak straight to the point"
  33,71,He will improve your actions for you and forgive you your sins. Anyone who obeys God and His messenger will achieve a splendid Triumph. God´s Trust; The Human Dilemma
  33,72,"We offered the trust to Heaven and Earth, and to the mountains too, yet they refused to carry it, and shrank back from it. However man accepted it: he has been unfair [to himself], ignorant"
  33,73,"Still God will punish hypocritical men and hypocritical women and associating men and associating women. However God relents with believing men and believing women. God is Forgiving, Merciful"